<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Wield" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Wield,</orth> to use with the hand, to manage: <cit><quote>weapons w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1432" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1432</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.1.101" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 1, 101</bibl>. <cit><quote>wilt thou the spigot w.?</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.3.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 3, 24</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to w. a sceptre,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.6.73" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 6, 73</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>more than words can w. the matter,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.1.56" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 1, 56</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>